long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ChatGPT Table Export allows you to streamline your workflow by providing you with a simply integrated "Export" button below every table, eliminating the need for tedious data reformatting.

ChatGPT Table Export supports both CSV and JSON formats for Excel users and data analytics. Speaking of Excel users, tables containing Excel formulas are fully supported using the CSV format and populate right into Excel as expected.

ChatGPT Table Exporter is available for a subscription price of $8 per year. Download, subscribe, and make your data more accessible than ever!
